    <section id="reviews" class="reviews-section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <p class="section-label">Testimonials</p>
            <h2>What Our Guests Say</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Real experiences from real guests who chose Demo Hotel.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reviews-grid">
            <div class="review-card">
                <div class="review-stars">
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                </div>
                <p class="review-text">"Absolutely stunning stay. The room was immaculate, staff were incredibly warm, and the views were breathtaking. Will definitely be returning on our next trip to the city."</p>
                <div class="review-author">
                    <div class="review-avatar">SR</div>
                    <div class="review-meta">
                        <strong>Sarah Rahman</strong>
                        <span>Business Traveller · New Delhi</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="review-platform"><i class="fab fa-google"></i> Google Review</div>
            </div>

            <div class="review-card review-card--featured">
                <div class="review-stars">
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                </div>
                <p class="review-text">"Perfect family getaway! The family suite was spacious and had everything we needed. Kids loved the pool. The restaurant food was exceptional. Highly recommended for families."</p>
                <div class="review-author">
                    <div class="review-avatar">MK</div>
                    <div class="review-meta">
                        <strong>Michael & Karen</strong>
                        <span>Family Stay · Mumbai</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="review-platform"><i class="fab fa-tripadvisor"></i> TripAdvisor</div>
            </div>

            <div class="review-card">
                <div class="review-stars">
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star-half-alt"></i>
                </div>
                <p class="review-text">"Great location, excellent service, and a very comfortable bed! The room service was prompt and the food was delicious. The spa treatment was the highlight of our anniversary stay."</p>
                <div class="review-author">
                    <div class="review-avatar">AP</div>
                    <div class="review-meta">
                        <strong>Ananya Patel</strong>
                        <span>Couple Stay · Bangalore</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="review-platform"><i class="fab fa-google"></i> Google Review</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reviews-summary">
            <div class="reviews-summary-score">
                <span class="score-num">4.9</span>
                <div class="score-stars">
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                </div>
